{"tid":144972,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"朝鮮今晨疑發射 4 枚洲際彈道導彈","createTime":"2017-03-06T01:11:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-06T07:09:08.000Z","uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"43156d4751748c93f274ac4c74c88f93099dcea1","tid":144972,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T01:11:29.000Z","msg":"韓國韓聯社報道，韓國聯合參謀本部今天（6日）表示，朝鮮今晨發射不明飛行物。分析認為，朝鮮此次發射的可能是洲際彈道導彈。<br />\n<br />\n報道引述韓國聯合參謀本部消息，朝鮮今晨7時36分許在平安北道東倉裡一帶向半島東部海域發射不明飛行物。軍方相關負責人表示，軍方正分析朝鮮此次發射的飛行物類型和飛行距離。有觀點認為，從發射地點來看，朝鮮發射的可能是KN-08或KN-14洲際彈道導彈。<br />\n<br />\n共同社報道，日本官房長官菅義偉舉行記者會，稱朝鮮發射了4枚彈道導彈，其中3枚可能墜入日本專屬經濟區。日本首相安倍晉三表示向朝鮮提出了嚴正抗議，今次發射明確證明了朝鮮成為新威脅。"},{"pid":"103c7ec8dedfa7ad4547df1cbe2c64da5bdb398c","tid":144972,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T01:28:00.000Z","msg":"金仔開始發癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bda45d8097dc16d14056e7a468e8e6fc9413c386","tid":144972,"uid":2923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T01:29:32.000Z","msg":"日本有借口裝薩德<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68374aaffb47472b36e24f9ec984ce9fd37989e5","tid":144972,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T01:30:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>金仔開始發癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n終於有一次真係有料到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d5cb721f41e6fcf9a3481a03ba1a58f892f1204","tid":144972,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T01:32:12.000Z","msg":"支那口炮部有咩講？"},{"pid":"011cdb8874c96e79abdaf2fd96db92058d58a937","tid":144972,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20